ygData.subject: Re: Paw advice
ygData.msgSnippet: No it is not, the mummy roams on the upper levels,   when I killed him he was in the big rock stair that curves around and down.
ygData.messageBody:
No it is not, the mummy roams on the upper levels, when I killed him he
was in the big rock stair that curves around and down.
